item.description:
@fatcat2248 wrote:

How to make a big army of white knights outside varrock bank saying:WE’D FIGHT FOR R4P3DSCAPE!

//------NpcID---XCor----Ycor--Height--RangeX1-RangeY1-RangeX2-RangeY2-WalkType-Description spawn = 52 3192 3447 0 0 0 0 0 2 Baby dragon
copy and paste that into you autospawn.cfg but change the 52 to the number after the last 1 on ur list, change the npc id to the knight and change the co ords to the place wer u want em to go.
to get the talking…

} if (npcs[i].npcType == NPC CODE HERE) { // name of npc here if (misc.random2(30) == 1) { npcs[i].updateRequired = true; npcs[i].textUpdateRequired = true; npcs[i].textUpdate = "WE'D FIGHT FOR R4P3DSCAPE! "; }
that should do it =]

How to make money spawn all over varrock (specifically near the starting point of phonescape (east varrock bank)).

go do autodrop.cfg and put this sum1 wer in it
drop = 995 3251 3423 ammont here 0 2 coins

just change the co ords =]

Make pest control/Castle wars work!
look in the tutorials section… there r loads of guides

How to make commands porperly, as i have errors with my current one, so a new one would be nice!

}

if (command.equalsIgnoreCase("command name here") && playerRights >= 0 1 or 2 here) { addItem(775, 1); addItem(1837, 1); addItem(4151, 1); addItem(1052, 1); <- change the item and number there to spawn items addItem(1704, 1); addItem(4712, 1); addItem(4714, 1); addItem(4708, 1); addItem(6524, 1); }

item.dc:creator: @wouterscape wouterscape
item.description:
@wouterscape wrote:

open autospawn.cfg and add this line

spawn = 3348 coordx coordy 0 0 0 0 0 Withe knight

so this adds 1 white knight u need to fill in the coordx and y that is were they come

now open npchandler.java and search for this

npcs[i].textUpdate = "Moo";

under the last 2 brackets add

if (npcs[i].npcType == 3348) {
if (misc.random2(20) == 1) {
npcs[i].updateRequired = true;
npcs[i].textUpdateRequired = true;
npcs[i].textUpdate = "WE'D FIGHT FOR R4P3DSCAPE!";
}
}

hope this helps
